<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>HumMatch Pricing | Find Songs That Match Your Voice</title>
  <meta name="description" content="HumMatch pricing. Free to start, unlimited with Squad Leader for just $7.99/month or $49.99/year."/>
  <link rel="icon" href="/hummatch-icon-bug-2x.png" type="image/png"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg: #0d0b1a;
      --white: #e2e0f0;
      --text-muted: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      --purple: #A855F7;
      --pink: #EC4899;
      --surface-border: rgba(124,58,237,0.12);
      --radius: 14px;
    }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    a { color: inherit; }

    /* NAV */
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 18px 24px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--pink));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 24px 20px;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .hero p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* PRICING GRID */
    .pricing-section {
      padding: 40px 24px 80px;
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 380px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    }

    .pricing-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 36px 28px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .pricing-card.featured {
      border-color: var(--purple);
      background: rgba(168,85,247,0.06);
    }
    .pricing-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A855F7, #EC4899);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .pricing-card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }
    .pricing-price {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .pricing-price span {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .pricing-sub {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .pricing-save {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(168,85,247,0.15);
      color: var(--purple);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .pricing-features {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .pricing-features li {
      padding: 8px 0;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      padding-left: 24px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .pricing-features li::before {
      content: "\2713";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--purple);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #a855f7);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    footer a { color: rgba(168,85,247,0.6); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--purple); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">HumMatch</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/">Try HumMatch</a>
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/squadmatch">SquadMatch</a>
    <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
    <a href="/dashboard" id="navLoginItem">Log In</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>Free to start. Unlimited with <span style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#A855F7,#EC4899);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">Squad Leader</span>.</h1>
  <p>Use HumMatch free to find songs for your voice. Upgrade to Squad Leader to unlock harmonic group song matching powered by your squad's vocal range, timbre, and brightness.</p>
</div>

<section class="pricing-section">
  <div class="pricing-grid">

    <!-- FREE -->
    <div class="pricing-card">
      <h3>Free</h3>
      <div class="pricing-price">$0</div>
      <div class="pricing-sub">&nbsp;</div>
      <ul class="pricing-features">
        <li>Join a squad for free</li>
        <li>Hum when invited by a Squad Leader</li>
        <li>View shared song results</li>
        <li>Save your setlist</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Started Free</a>
    </div>

    <!-- PREMIUM MONTHLY -->
    <div class="pricing-card">
      <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#A855F7,#EC4899);color:#fff;font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:0.08em;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:12px;text-transform:uppercase;">SQUAD LEADER TIER</div>
      <h3 style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#A855F7,#EC4899);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">Squad Leader Monthly</h3>
      <div class="pricing-price">$7<span>.99 / mo</span></div>
      <div class="pricing-sub">Billed monthly</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:4px;line-height:1.4;">Squad Leader unlocks harmonic group song matching powered by your squad's vocal range, timbre, and brightness.</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.76rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-bottom:14px;">Plus utilities:</div>
      <ul class="pricing-features">
        <li>Unlimited hums & SquadMatch sessions</li>
        <li>Invite up to 4 friends per session</li>
        <li>Squad HQ with shared playlists</li>
        <li>Issue up to 5 exclusive 20% discount codes</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/api/hummatch/checkout/monthly" class="btn btn-primary">Become a Squad Leader</a>
    </div>

    <!-- PREMIUM ANNUAL -->
    <div class="pricing-card featured">
      <div class="pricing-badge">BEST VALUE</div>
      <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#A855F7,#EC4899);color:#fff;font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:0.08em;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:12px;text-transform:uppercase;">SQUAD LEADER TIER</div>
      <h3 style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#A855F7,#EC4899);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;">Squad Leader Annual</h3>
      <div class="pricing-price">$49<span>.99 / yr</span></div>
      <div class="pricing-sub">Billed annually</div>
      <div class="pricing-save">Save 48%!</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:4px;line-height:1.4;">Squad Leader unlocks harmonic group song matching powered by your squad's vocal range, timbre, and brightness.</div>
      <div style="font-size:0.76rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-bottom:14px;">Plus utilities:</div>
      <ul class="pricing-features">
        <li>Unlimited hums & SquadMatch sessions</li>
        <li>Invite up to 4 friends per session</li>
        <li>Squad HQ with shared playlists</li>
        <li>Issue up to 5 exclusive 20% discount codes</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/api/hummatch/checkout/annual" class="btn btn-primary">Become a Squad Leader, Save 45%</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2026 HumMatch &middot; <a href="/">Try HumMatch</a> &middot; <a href="/squadmatch">SquadMatch</a> &middot; <a href="/contact">Contact</a> &middot; <a href="/blog">Blog</a> &middot; <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> &middot; <a href="/terms">Terms</a></p>
</footer>
<script>
(function(){
  var t = localStorage.getItem('hm_dash_token');
  if(t){
    var nav = document.getElementById('navLoginItem');
    if(nav){ nav.textContent='My HQ'; }
  }
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
